                            <comment id="13414384" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Sat, 14 Jul 2012 12:38:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The Javadoc says:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Only call this method after a connection has been opened&lt;br/&gt;
by &lt;/p&gt;
{@link #connect connect()}
&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s not possible to initialise the socket when creating FTPClient.&lt;br/&gt;
Use SocketClient.setDefaultTimeout(int timeout) instead.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
